== 反響 ==
[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]新鮮度僅11%，基於122條評論，平均分為2.8/10<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/dirty_grandpa/ |title=Dirty Grandpa (2016) |website=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] |accessdate=January 22, 2016 |archive-date=2016-01-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160125233734/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/dirty_grandpa/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]得分只有18<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/dirty-grandpa |title=Dirty Grandpa reviews |website=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |accessdate=January 22, 2016 |archive-date=2016-01-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160125222802/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/dirty-grandpa |dead-url=no }}</ref>；[[IMDB|IMDB]]得分6.0，差評佔大多數，甚至被許多影評人認為是2016年最糟的電影之一。

影評人膝關節表示這部不要以去審視的心態去看，雖然有略顯低俗下流的橋段，包裝成人與青少年的集體焦慮，不說教也不閃躲扭捏，在看似胡搞瞎鬧的片段裡，還有一絲溫馨。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://m.nownews.com/news/1968785 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2017-04-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170423152201/https://m.nownews.com/news/1968785 |archive-date=2017-04-23 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

